Metadata.Title: Salsipuedes
Metadata.Description: Good afternoon 47Your primary target is Manny Russo, a human trafficker who has escaped death in the argentinian border after a different assassin got sloppy and killed the wrong person, him and two journalists he has kidnapped are currently in Mendoza,Your secondary target is Sandro Tarella and his crew who helped Manny get his hands on the journalists to begin withWe do not know the whereabouts of the journalists however, we do know that  Manny plans on executing them soon as a request from an unknown customer of his. Our client says this cannot happen and has demanded that we eliminate the targets before Manny can give the go order to kill the journalists.Good luck 47, I'll leave you to prepare.
